      <title>印度通胀率自 2019 年以来首次跌破印度储备银行目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/india-inflation-dips-below-rbi-target-for-first-time-since-2019</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度通胀率近五年来首次低于央行目标，但由于政策制定者希望看到价格持续下降，因此目前不太可能刺激降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/india-inflation-dips-below-rbi-target-for-first-time-since-2019</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 12:10:12 GMT</pubDate>
